<div class="col-md-8">
  <div class="widget">
    <div class="widget-heading">
      <h5>We have received your information and we are in the process of finding the best tutor for you!</h5>
    </div>
    <div class="widget-body">
      A <b>TopTutoring</b> representative will contact you within the next <b>24 hours</b>,
      by phone or by email, and get you connected with your new tutor.
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="widget">
    <div class="widget-heading">
      <h5>Got some downtime?</h5>
      <h5>There's still plenty you can do while you wait!</h5>
    </div>
    <div class="widget-body">
      <ul>
        <li>
          <%= link_to "Tell us your availability!", new_availability_path %> This can speed up the process of finding
          you a tutor and will help us pick a tutor that is a perfect fit for your schedule.
        </li>
        <li>
          Check out the <%= link_to "TopTutoring Blog", 'https://toptutoring.com/blog/' %>. We talk about current news
          in the learning world, tips and tricks to help you get the most out of your tutoring sessions, and some great
          advice from tutors and students who want to help you succeed. Everything is written
          by our very own <b>TopTutoring</b> gurus with years of experience in the world of tutoring.
        </li>
        <li>
          Pre-pay for your first hour with your tutor. Pre-Paying for your first hour with your tutor will speed up the
          sign-up process and keeps <b>TopTutoring</b> and its clients safe from illegitamate transactions. If you'd like
          to get a head-start, check out our pre-payment options over <%= link_to "here", "#" %>.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="widget">
    <div class="widget-heading">
      <h5>Have any more questions or concerns?</h5>
      Please let us know!

      If necessary, a more detailed and formal message can be sent to us <%= link_to "here", 'https://toptutoring.com/contact/' %>.
    </div>

    <div class="widget-body">
      <%= form_for users_clients_path(current_user) do |form| %>
        <%= form.fields_for :client_info do |client_field| %>
          <%= client_field.text_area :comments, placeholder: "COMMENTS", rows: "3", style: "height:100px; margin-top: 25px;" %>
        <% end %>
          <button type="submit" style="color: #888888;">Send comment</button>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
